      "text": "— Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) March 15, 2017 Snoop Dogg has again used his music in order to attack President Donald Trump, with the release of a new song entitled “Make America Crip Again.”The rapper — real name is Calvin Broadus Jr. — says in the opening lines of the song that “the president said he wants to make America great again.” F*ck - Sh*t - America - Crip “F*ck that sh*t, we’re going to make America crip again,” it continues.The song then takes aim at Trump’s comments on the scandal currently engulfing the NFL, in which he called for football players who decide to take a knee during the National Anthem to be fired, and also defends former San Francisco 49ers quarterback Colin Kaepernick, who popularized the form of Anthem protest during the 2016-17 season. Millionaires - Skin - Mine “As I look around I see so many millionaires with skin like mine,... (Excerpt) Read more at: Breitbart 1 other people are viewing this story",
