      "text": "Watch our political team in a live discussion about the upcoming election at noon Tuesday at The Press’ Facebook page, facebook.com/PressofAC . Latest Video \nDuring the discussion, we will take readers’ questions and preview the 2nd Legislative District debate Wednesday night at Stockton University. The debate is co-sponsored by The Press of Atlantic City and the William J. Hughes Center for Public Policy. \nA one-hour debate will start at 6 p.m. between Senate candidates Chris Brown, a Republican, and Colin Bell, a Democrat. After a half-hour break, a one-hour debate among Assembly candidates will start at 7:30 p.m. with incumbent Vince Mazzeo and John Armato, both Democrats, and Vince Sera and Brenda Taube, both Republicans. Stay informed! Sign up to receive top headlines delivered to your inbox each morning. \nContact: 609-272-7046",
